about.summary: Routines for the analysis of nonlinear time series. This work is largely inspired by the TISEAN project, by Rainer Hegger, Holger Kantz and Thomas Schreiber: <http://www.mpipks-dresden.mpg.de/~tisean/>.

name: r-tserieschaos
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '0.1-13.1' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-tserieschaos
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/tseriesChaos_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/tseriesChaos/tseriesChaos_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 23cb5fea56409a305e02a523ff8b7642ec383942d415c9cffdc92208dacfd961

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1

  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]

  host:
    - r-base
    - r-desolve

  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-desolve

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('tseriesChaos')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('tseriesChaos')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=tseriesChaos
  license: GPL-2
  summary: 'Routines for the analysis of nonlinear time series. This work is largely inspired
    by the TISEAN project, by Rainer Hegger, Holger Kantz and Thomas Schreiber: <http://www.mpipks-dresden.mpg.de/~tisean/>.'

  license_family: GPL2
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - PackageCondaDataScience
